snippet.title: Honey Pot | Coming soon
snippet.description:
Dive into the immersive world of 'Honey Pot,' a cooperative action-strategy VR game where you and your friends become bees defending the hive from bears on the hunt. 

Fly, gather honey, construct turrets, deploy stingers, and use bow and arrow attacks in a frantic battle to protect Queen Bee Melli's domain. 

Team up, strategize, and save the hive in this thrilling VR experience!
